253470/extras/11335caf7d398b9a1c5018d21f6b007d.poster.avif?t=1708505018\" width=615 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253470/extras/11335caf7d398b9a1c5018d21f6b007d.webm?t=1708505018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253470/extras/6c923f12defcf58add9572833fef6164.avif?t=1708505018\" width=615 height=90 /></span><br>Collect bugcats books, many unknown Capoo and bugcats are waiting for you to discover and collect.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253470/extras/9a0c2edf9dafc2ef6a167f1de6476533.poster.avif?t=1708505018\" width=616 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253470/extras/9a0c2edf9dafc2ef6a167f1de6476533.webm?t=1708505018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253470/extras/9a0c2edf9dafc2ef6a167f1de6476533.mp4?t=1708505018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Let's think~ </h2></strong><br>Does it make you feel lonely when you are alone with your computer?<br>Are you tired of the same presentations and information on the screen when you go to work?<br>Feeling drained when you've been working on your term report all day?<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >At this time, let Capoo and the bugcats accompany you to restore your vitality~</h2></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Now, the popular and cute Capoo &amp; bugcats are officially knocking on your door! </strong></h2>Capoo will bring all kinds of bugcats to accompany you through every moment in front of the computer screen<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253470/extras/413f104119bcb1d7dd94e038c50db76f.avif?t=1708505018\" width=615 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong> Capoo and the bugcats , with the wallpaper of Capoo outdoor event, will make you full of energy every day! <strong><br><strong> Interact with the Capoo on the desktop and let their funny expressions keep you in a good mood! <strong><br><strong>Assisting Capoo to clean up the poop on the desktop can make them change from helpless to happy<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now, let Capoo and the bugcats become good partners on your screen and desktop! </strong></h2></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong>",
